Production switch (recommended)

Set these to true in orchestrator/.env when ready:

AUTH_REQUIRED=true
AUTHZ_ENFORCE_SCOPES=true
AUTHZ_REQUIRE_WORKSPACE=true
Then configure:

JWT_SECRET (or JWT_PUBLIC_KEY)
JWT_ISSUER
JWT_AUDIENCE
Optional tracing: LANGFUSE_* / HELICONE_*
Optional billing: STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
